  "originalContent": "<div id=\"readme\" class=\"md\" data-path=\"README.md\"><article class=\"markdown-body entry-content container-lg\" itemprop=\"text\"><div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h1 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">extended_nested_scroll_view</h1><a id=\"user-content-extended_nested_scroll_view\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: extended_nested_scroll_view\" href=\"#extended_nested_scroll_view\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://pub.dartlang.org/packages/extended_nested_scroll_view\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/2d405e4c4398fd3ecd330d264075575393bb6da8d0fb6f69d5f78d2bfa8727c3/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f7075622f762f657874656e6465645f6e65737465645f7363726f6c6c5f766965772e737667\" alt=\"pub package\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/pub/v/extended_nested_scroll_view.svg\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/stargazers\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/68ed40ec583b78365d1f2254e73837d0b08bb0612277b3a030b7da7f1970d9b8/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f73746172732f666c757474657263616e646965732f657874656e6465645f6e65737465645f7363726f6c6c5f76696577\" alt=\"GitHub stars\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/network\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/0fca59d54986ac14974ba72e22735d285b0fdf164096b03dfebce2e71dd82e26/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f666f726b732f666c757474657263616e646965732f657874656e6465645f6e65737465645f7363726f6c6c5f76696577\" alt=\"GitHub forks\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/forks/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a>  <a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/blob/master/LICENSE\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/558ed1da94412ed51999ca76cc4c387097b9d657708a989641534d2b3657c1f5/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f6c6963656e73652f666c757474657263616e646965732f657874656e6465645f6e65737465645f7363726f6c6c5f76696577\" alt=\"GitHub license\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a>  <a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/issues\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f6c50279c99bb13766eb10e6a20955f34a3021b9277cf4a588af27130fdfbaa0/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f6973737565732f666c757474657263616e646965732f657874656e6465645f6e65737465645f7363726f6c6c5f76696577\" alt=\"GitHub issues\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/issues/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a> <a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/q/ZyJbSVjfSU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.\" alt=\"FlutterCandies QQ 群\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/yaml?url=https%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Ffluttercandies%2F.github%2Frefs%2Fheads%2Fmain%2Fdata.yml&amp;query=%24.qq_group_number&amp;label=QQ%E7%BE%A4&amp;logo=qq&amp;color=1DACE8\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Language: <a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/blob/HEAD/README.md\">English</a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/blob/HEAD/README-ZH.md\">中文简体</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">NestedScrollView: extended nested scroll view to fix following issues.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">1.<a href=\"https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/22393\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/flutter/flutter/issues/22393/hovercard\">pinned sliver header issue</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">2.<a href=\"https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/21868\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/flutter/flutter/issues/21868/hovercard\">inner scrollables in tabview sync issue</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">3.do without ScrollController in NestedScrollView's body</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://fluttercandies.github.io/extended_nested_scroll_view/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Web demo for ExtendedNestedScrollView</a></p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><a href=\"#extended_nested_scroll_view\">extended_nested_scroll_view</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#example-for-issue-1\">Example for issue 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#example-for-issue-2\">Example for issue 2</a>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><a href=\"#extendedvisibilitydetector\">ExtendedVisibilityDetector</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#do-without-scrollcontroller-in-nestedscrollviews-body\">Do without ScrollController in NestedScrollView's body</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h1 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Example for issue 1</h1><a id=\"user-content-example-for-issue-1\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Example for issue 1\" href=\"#example-for-issue-1\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">give total height of pinned sliver headers in pinnedHeaderSliverHeightBuilder callback</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-dart notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\" var tabBarHeight = primaryTabBar.preferredSize.height;\n      var pinnedHeaderHeight =\n          //statusBar height\n          statusBarHeight +\n              //pinned SliverAppBar height in header\n              kToolbarHeight;\n\n    ExtendedNestedScrollView(\n        pinnedHeaderSliverHeightBuilder: () {\n          return pinnedHeaderHeight;\n        }\n       )   ,\n       \"><pre> <span class=\"pl-k\">var</span> tabBarHeight <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> primaryTabBar.preferredSize.height;\n      <span class=\"pl-k\">var</span> pinnedHeaderHeight <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span>\n          <span class=\"pl-c\">//statusBar height</span>\n          statusBarHeight <span class=\"pl-k\">+</span>\n              <span class=\"pl-c\">//pinned SliverAppBar height in header</span>\n              kToolbarHeight;\n\n    <span class=\"pl-c1\">ExtendedNestedScrollView</span>(\n        pinnedHeaderSliverHeightBuilder<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> () {\n          <span class=\"pl-k\">return</span> pinnedHeaderHeight;\n        }\n       )   ,\n       </pre></div>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h1 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Example for issue 2</h1><a id=\"user-content-example-for-issue-2\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Example for issue 2\" href=\"#example-for-issue-2\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">We usually keep list scroll position with following:</p>\n<markdown-accessiblity-table><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>scene</th>\n<th>onlyOneScrollInBody</th>\n<th>description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>AutomaticKeepAliveClientMixin</td>\n<td>true</td>\n<td>ScrollPosition will not be disposed, set onlyOneScrollInBody to true so that we can know which list is isActived.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>PageStorageKey</td>\n<td>false</td>\n<td>ScrollPosition will be disposed, PageStorageKey just record the position info,the scroll positions in ExtendedNestedScrollView will always single one.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></markdown-accessiblity-table>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-dart notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"    ExtendedNestedScrollView(\n       onlyOneScrollInBody: true,\n    )\"><pre>    <span class=\"pl-c1\">ExtendedNestedScrollView</span>(\n       onlyOneScrollInBody<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">true</span>,\n    )</pre></div>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h2 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">ExtendedVisibilityDetector</h2><a id=\"user-content-extendedvisibilitydetector\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: ExtendedVisibilityDetector\" href=\"#extendedvisibilitydetector\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Provide ExtendedVisibilityDetector to point out which list is visible</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-dart notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"   ExtendedVisibilityDetector(\n      uniqueKey: const Key('Tab1'),\n      child: ListView(),\n   )\"><pre>   <span class=\"pl-c1\">ExtendedVisibilityDetector</span>(\n      uniqueKey<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Key</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">'Tab1'</span>),\n      child<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">ListView</span>(),\n   )</pre></div>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h1 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Do without ScrollController in NestedScrollView's body</h1><a id=\"user-content-do-without-scrollcontroller-in-nestedscrollviews-body\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Do without ScrollController in NestedScrollView's body\" href=\"#do-without-scrollcontroller-in-nestedscrollviews-body\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">due to we can't set ScrollController for list in NestedScrollView's body(it will breaking behaviours of InnerScrollController in NestedScrollView),provide Demos</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/tree/master/example/lib/pages/complex/pull_to_refresh.dart\">pull to refresh</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/tree/master/example/lib/pages/complex/load_more.dart\">load more</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/tree/master/example/lib/pages/complex/scroll_to_top.dart\">scroll to top</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">show how to do it without ScrollController</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://github.com/fluttercandies/extended_nested_scroll_view/tree/master/example/lib/pages/simple/dynamic_pinned_header_height.dart\">pinned header height</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">show how to change pinned header height dynamically.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</article></div>"
